Plot: A woman looks back at the past nineteen men she's had relationships with in her life and wonders if one of them might be her one true love.
Title: What's Your Number?
Writer: Gabrielle Allan (screenplay), Jennifer Crittenden (screenplay), Karyn Bosnak (novel)
Actors: Anna Faris, Chris Evans, Ari Graynor, Blythe Danner
tomatoConsensus: The comic timing of Anna Faris is sharp as always, but it's wasted away in this predictable, boilerplate comedy.
